featured.text: Where is Eleanor’s letter sent to? (A)
Sincerely yours, Eleanor Lightly Spokeswoman and Company Hair Stylist ABC Activity Insurance: Insure against overdoing it 41.

definition.zh_def: 埃莉諾，一個女性名字，源自法語，常用於英語國家。
definition.en_def: Eleanor, a female given name of French origin, commonly used in English-speaking countries.
definition.example: Eleanor decided to pursue a career in medicine.
